text: The 1926 Nevada gubernatorial election was held on November 2, 1926. Republican nominee Fred B. Balzar defeated Democratic incumbent James G. Scrugham with 53.00% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== *Fred B. Balzar, Republican *James G. Scrugham, Democratic ===Results=== ==References== 1926 Nevada Gubernatorial
title: 1926 Nevada gubernatorial election
